<p>Have Mac or iOS questions or problems that you just can&rsquo;t figure out? Mac Geek Gab has your answers. Submit your questions to&nbsp;Dave &amp; John and they&rsquo;ll dig in and get you your answer. Want to know <a href="http://www.macobserver.com/tmo/forums/viewthread/82689/" data-wpel-link="internal">how to safely move your iTunes library</a>? Need to find duplicate files on your hard drives? Is <a href="http://www.macobserver.com/tmo/answers/how_to_setup_gmail_imap_and_mail.app1/" data-wpel-link="internal">Gmail&rsquo;s &ldquo;All Mail&rdquo; folder confusing your Mac&rsquo;s Mail.app</a>? Listeners just like you wrote in with these questions this week and they got answers. You can hear the answers, too &mdash; it&rsquo;s free! Just press play, or even download and queue up for your next commute. What are you waiting for?</p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="center" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.macobserver.com/imgs/dave/macGeekGab02.jpg?resize=230%2C230" border="0" width="230" height="230" /></p>
